@startuml
actor User
participant Website
participant "Flask API" as API
participant APIFree
User -> Website: Submit preferences
activate Website
Website -> Website: Validate input
alt valid
Website -> API: POST /api/itinerary
activate API
API --> Website: Itinerary response
deactivate API
Website -> Website: Render activities
Website -> API: GET /api/image
activate API
API -> APIFree: POST /generate-image
activate APIFree
APIFree --> API: Image data
deactivate APIFree
API --> Website: Image response
deactivate API
Website -> User: Display itinerary and image
deactivate Website
else invalid
Website --> User: Show error 400
deactivate Website
end
@enduml